IMCOM v0.2.7   Copyright 2010-13 Barnaby Rowe
=============================================

Within this package please see imcom_documentation.pdf for light documentation
describing how to use this prototype v0.2.7 of the IMCOM (IMage COMbination)
software, described in Rowe, Hirata & Rhodes (2011;
http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2011ApJ...741...46R).

For all theoretical details and a precise description of what the IMCOM software
does, please see that paper.

Other papers that make use of IMCOM to explore image reconstruction from
undersampled data:

http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2013MNRAS.431.3103C
http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2013arXiv1310.3339S

General queries may be directed towards barnaby.t.p.rowe@gmail.com, although
Barney offers no guarantees about being able to provide useful responses!
